&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/APAC-TOKYO-TAKAZAWA-OFFER-LOGO-FINAL.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-5264&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/APAC-TOKYO-TAKAZAWA-OFFER-LOGO-FINAL.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;APAC- TOKYO- TAKAZAWA- OFFER- LOGO FINAL&quot; width=&quot;150&quot; height=&quot;27&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theworlds50best.com/asia/en/asias-50-best-restaurants/3140/takazawa.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-5156&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/MEDIA-50BestASIA_2014_logo2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;50BestASIA_2014_logo&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;86&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Located in the Akasaka section of Tokyo and set in an intimate, contemporary dining room of warm woods, each night only 10 diners have the privilege to experience the cuisine of Chef Yoshiaki Takazawa. Restaurant Takazawa has earned &lt;strong&gt;#31 on&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Asia&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants. &lt;/strong&gt;Dressy attire; jackets and ties are required for gentlemen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online on the &lt;a title=&quot;Takazawa&quot; href=&quot;http://www.takazawa-y.co.jp/reservation-en/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Takazawa website&lt;/a&gt; or contact Takazawa by phone at +81-03-3505-5052 from 14:00- 21:00 Tokyo time or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:reservation@takazawa-y.co.jp&quot;&gt;reservation@takazawa-y.co.jp&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time and either a cell phone number or a local number in Tokyo where the restaurant can reach you if necessary. Also provide any details if this is a special occasion or if there are allergies for any of the guests dining.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Takazawa requires reconfirmation of all reservations 4 days prior to the dining date. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If a reconfirmation is not received, the reservations will be cancelled. &nbsp;In the event of non-attendance, a late amendment or late cancellation, Takazawa reserves the right to charge a penalty fee that will be disclosed at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

